01:19.420 --> 01:25.760
Together, they've co-authored several books, including The New Science of UFOs and The Shadow of Time,

01:26.100 --> 01:33.780
a book involving ancient archaeological objects with anomalous properties being systematically excavated by private corporations.

01:33.780 --> 01:35.820
This thing's a cover-up.

01:36.440 --> 01:40.400
So when I found out that a former NSA director of research,

01:40.620 --> 01:45.440
who is privy to just about every sensitive piece of intelligence in the United States,

01:45.600 --> 01:49.900
wrote a book about anomalous objects being recovered in the desert,

01:50.200 --> 01:51.920
I had to reach out and learn more.

01:52.360 --> 01:55.960
Do you guys have kind of a base case for what's going on?

01:56.040 --> 02:02.420
