02:45:08.740 --> 02:45:15.960
So maybe that dialogue between that part of our body and the brain.

02:45:16.480 --> 02:45:24.360
And it's fantastic to, for me, it's fantastic to create a dialogue between the, like,

02:45:24.640 --> 02:45:28.320
several parts of the body.

